              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Phase 4 m7-006: match expressions on enum types must cover every variant. Either add the missing variant arms or use a wildcard pattern `_` to catch the remainder. Diagnostic code lands in the type-system pattern region (0500-0899) — the issue spec's M0900 was out of M's reserved range (0300-0499); T0512 follows m1-003's T0511 reservation for the future borrowed-reference codepath."
