              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Phase 4 m9-005: trait-bound resolution. At this call site, a method requires its type argument to implement a specific trait, but neither a generic-parameter bound nor a concrete impl satisfies this requirement. Either bind the type parameter to the required trait in the enclosing generic-parameter list, or provide a concrete impl for the type."
